function Start()

	idKatoClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idKato, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idKatoClone) then

		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idKatoClone, trigKatoLeave, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idKatoClone)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idKatoClone)
		Hydra.EventSend("DebtRepaid_KatoCleanup", idSelf)
		
	end

	-- Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idKato)

end
